item.title: US-89A South at AZ-389
item.description: US-89A South at AZ-389 in Fredonia. Turn right on AZ-389 west for Colorado City, Hurricane (Utah), and Pipe Spring National Monument. Continue south on US-89A for Jacob Lake.

item.title: US-89 North at US-89A
item.description: US-89 north at US-89A. Turn left for US-89A; right to continue north on US-89. Until recently US-89A in Utah was marked as UT-11.

item.title: US-89 North Approaching US-89A
item.description: US-89 North approaching US-89A in Kanab.

item.title: US-89 North Approaching US-89A
item.description: US-89 North approaching US-89A. Use US-89A south for Fredonia, Jacob Lake, and Grand Canyon (all destinations in Arizona). Continue north on US-89 north for Panguitch, Zion National Park, and Bryce Canyon National Park.

item.title: End US-89A South at US-89
item.description: End US-89A south at US-89 to Page and Flagstaff.

item.title: US-89A North - Jacob Lake
item.description: Entering Jacob Lake on US-89A north. Elevation 7,921.

item.title: US-89 South Approaching US-89A
item.description: US-89 south at US-89A. Turn right for US-89A north to Fredonia and Kanab, UT. Continue on US-89 south for Flagstaff.

item.title: US-89 South at US-89A
item.description: US-89 south approaching US-89A. Turn right for US-89A north.

item.title: AZ-67 North Approaching US-89A
item.description: End AZ-67 at US-89A in Jacob Lake. US-89A incorrectly signed as AZ-89A.

item.title: End AZ-67 North at US-89A
item.description: End AZ-67 at US-89A in Jacob Lake.

item.title: End AZ-67 North at US-89A
item.description: End AZ-67 north at US-89A junction, to Fredonia and Flagstaff, in Jacob Lake.

item.title: End US-89A South at US-89
item.description: Southern terminous of US-89A at US-89 to Page and Flagstaff

item.title: Jct. US-89 on US-89A South
item.description: Junction US-89 1/2 mile at southern terminous of US-89A South.

item.title: US-89 South at UT-11 to US-89A
item.description: US-89 at UT-11 junction in Kanab. UT-11 turns into US-89A at the Arizona Line.
